2. Go to your Jellyfin **Admin Dashboard** in your web browser
3. Navigate to **Dashboard â†’ General â†’ Custom CSS**
4. Copy & paste the CSS code from the `jellyfin-plugin-ratings` folder
5. For JavaScript tweaks, paste into **Dashboard â†’ General â†’ Custom JavaScript**
6. Click **Save** and hard refresh your browser (Ctrl+Shift+R / Cmd+Shift+R)
